data.text:
The Alaska annual awards seek to extend recognition to those who give their time and effort to the organization by way of service. Alaska Youth Soccer awards and recognizes those individuals at the AYSA Annual General Meeting.

Alaska Youth Soccer recognizes individuals in the following categories: Volunteer of the Year, Administrator of the Year, Coach of the Year Recreational (boy & girl), Coach of the Year Competitive (boy & girl), TOPSoccer Coach of the Year, TOPSoccer Buddy of the Year, Young Referee of the Year (female & male).

Alaska Youth Soccer has our Annual General Meeting and Award Recognition every November.
